03:27.415 --> 03:28.541
Why'd you do it?

03:32.170 --> 03:33.296
I don't know.

03:33.922 --> 03:38.635
Okay. Well, see,
now, that's not gonna cut it.

03:40.553 --> 03:43.056
-Well, sorry.
-Well, Jeff…

03:45.183 --> 03:46.809
I don't need you to say sorry.

03:50.521 --> 03:51.898
I need to know why.

03:53.024 --> 03:56.152
Because there needs
to be some responsibility here.

03:56.236 --> 04:00.865
What you've done to the family,
to Grandma, to Shari and me.

04:01.950 --> 04:03.117
Mm.

04:04.410 --> 04:05.578
I mean, do you--?

04:08.915 --> 04:11.209
Do you have any idea how this all started?

04:13.503 --> 04:14.671
I don't know.

04:17.048 --> 04:20.593
I mean, I been… thinking about it.

04:21.803 --> 04:22.762
A lot.

04:24.555 --> 04:25.723
You know?

04:29.310 --> 04:30.561
So I used to…

04:34.816 --> 04:35.817
Well…

04:37.610 --> 04:41.197
Remember when you used to take me
to go and find roadkill

04:41.281 --> 04:43.324
and we'd cut 'em up?

04:43.408 --> 04:44.701
No, no, no, .

04:46.244 --> 04:48.496
You're not gonna lay this on me, no.

04:48.579 --> 04:50.957
No.

04:51.040 --> 04:51.916
'Kay.

04:52.000 --> 04:53.376
It's not my fault.

04:53.459 --> 04:54.627
