that Joyce tried to kill herself.

41:57.640 --> 41:58.974
Oh, Jesus.

42:00.684 --> 42:01.936
Oh, Jesus.

42:06.398 --> 42:07.274
She's okay, though?

42:08.651 --> 42:09.527
Yeah.

42:10.236 --> 42:11.070
Okay.

42:13.656 --> 42:14.657
I'll call him.

42:30.756 --> 42:31.757
Thank you, guys.

42:33.676 --> 42:35.678
We're glad to be back on the force.

42:36.220 --> 42:38.430
Thank you, uh, for all your support.

42:39.890 --> 42:42.643
It's meant a lot, and, uh…

42:44.019 --> 42:46.438
it was nice to know
that somebody has your back.

42:46.522 --> 42:47.648
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

42:50.401 --> 42:51.694
-Thank you.
-Thanks.

42:51.777 --> 42:54.238
-Good to see you, sir. How are you?
-Bobby!

42:54.321 --> 42:56.574
