go back to Jeffrey Dahmer,

43:12.172 --> 43:13.924
they've just been reinstated.

43:14.008 --> 43:14.883
What?

43:15.759 --> 43:17.720
A slap on the wrist and that's it?

43:17.803 --> 43:20.055
Mayor said
they're gonna appeal the decision.

43:20.139 --> 43:21.682
And if that fails?

43:23.267 --> 43:25.144
Then we…

43:26.228 --> 43:27.730
…fight the next fight.

43:29.315 --> 43:30.649
And the next fight.

43:34.695 --> 43:35.821
And the next.
